1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Bc4 Nf6 5. f3 exf3 (5... Bf5 6. fxe4 { If we can, get the bishop pair. } 6... Nxe4 7. Qf3 Nxc3 { Pause. } (7... Nd6 { The only good move. } 8. Bxf7+ Kxf7 9. g4) 8. Bxf7+ Kxf7 9. Qxf5+ Ke8 10. bxc3) 6. Nxf3 Bf5 (6... e6 { Passive... boring... let's mess things up! } 7. O-O Be7 8. Qe1 O-O 9. Bd3 Nbd7 10. Qh4 { This is equal but very hard for black. } 10... h6 (10... g6 11. Bg5 b6 12. Ne5 Nxe5 13. dxe5 { Magic! }) 11. Bxh6 gxh6 12. Qxh6 Re8 13. Ng5 Nf8 14. Rf3) 7. O-O e6 8. Ng5 h6 (8... Be7 9. Rxf5 exf5 10. Nxf7) (8... Bg6 { The only good move... but we have an idea! } 9. Bxe6 fxe6 10. Nxe6 Qd7 11. Bg5 Qxe6 12. Bxf6 gxf6 13. Re1) 9. Nxf7 Kxf7 10. Rxf5 Ke7 11. Qe2 *


